ygData.messageBody:
Salutations!

Hi Mary Beth, I'm Brangvyne (yes that's my real name)
and just wanted to say hi and welcome to the list.

I play a 62 high elf Cleric (Melwen), a 55 wood elf
druid (Xenawyr), a 52 wood elf ranger (Brangvyne), a
35 dark elf shadow knight (Moriel), a 33 dark elf
enchanter (Linnathon), and a 31 wood elf bard
(Banderette) all on the Xegony server. I have a 3 half
elf bard (Brangvyne) on the Chazic Thule server as
well but as you can see I have not played her much.

Good luck on your paper for college and I'd be happy
to answer questions or whatever if you want and think
it will help you in any way. Either here or e-mail is
fine. (Brangyvne7@...).

/Hugs
Bran

--- Mary Beth <lilock@...> wrote:
> Hello,
>
> I'm Mary Beth and I play a 65 Dark Elf Cleric
> (Brinni) and a 65
> Human Monk (Naiya) on the Ayonae Ro server. I
> belong to the guild
> Legend of the Jokers www.lotj.net and I have just
> ran across this
> mailing list. I would love to be a part of it and
> meet some new
> everquest players; female ones at that!
>
> I should also mention that I am doing a University
> paper on the
> women of everquest. The other reason I decided to
> join this mail
> list is to get some opinions from other women who
> play everquest and
> what it means to them to be involved in this type of
> mporpg. If
> anyone is interested in finding more information out
> about my
> research paper and wouldn't mind answering a few
> questions, feel
> free to contact me either through here or privately.
>
>
> Thanks and I look forward to meeting all of you!
> ~Mary Beth
>
>
>
